You have chosen choice %s''' % PlayerChoice)
        print('%s quietly approach the cell door and queitly open the door.'% CharName)
    elif PlayerChoice=="3":
        print('''
You have chosen choice %s''' % PlayerChoice)
        print('%s jolts upward and run toward the cell bars. You shake them violently and yell out for help.'% CharName)
    elif PlayerChoice=="4":
        print('''
You have chosen choice %s''' % PlayerChoice)
        print('After waking up you decide that it is just a nightmare and decide to go back to sleep.')
        print('You wake up to a dark figure standing over you, the figure brandishes something with a bright reflecttion. The figure thrusts at you and your vision goes dark')
        print('''
    I----------I
    I   Game   I
    I   Over   I
    I    !!    I
    I----------I''')
    elif PlayerChoice=="5":
        print('''
You have chosen choice %s''' % PlayerChoice)
